---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Kinevra - SAP Integration Experts" description="Learn about Kinevra's mission to transform enterprises through expert SAP integration and Business Technology Platform solutions.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="blur-bg blur-bg-1"></div>
    <div class="blur-bg blur-bg-2"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero-content">
        <h1 class="gradient-text animate-slide-up">About Kinevra</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
          One developer. Years of SAP experience. Zero corporate BS.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <div class="content-block animate-slide-up">
            <h2>The Story</h2>
            <p>
              After years working with big consulting firms, I noticed something: clients were paying fortune for simple SAP work 
              that took forever to deliver. Teams of 20 people for a 2-person job. Meetings about meetings. You know the drill.
            </p>
            <p>
              So I started Kinevra. It's just me, which means when you hire us, you get someone who actually knows SAP, 
              writes the code themselves, and responds to emails the same day. Revolutionary concept, I know.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block animate-slide-up">
            <h2>How I Work</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                    <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Fast Turnaround</h3>
                <p>Most fixes within 48 hours. Bigger projects get realistic timelines that I actually stick to.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/>
                    <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/>
                    <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/>
                    <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/>
                    <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Clear Pricing</h3>
                <p>You'll know the cost upfront. No surprise invoices or mysterious "scope changes."</p>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
                    <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Real Communication</h3>
                <p>I answer emails myself. No ticketing systems, no "your call is important to us."</p>
              </div>
              <div class="feature-item glass-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                  <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M9 11H3v10h6V11z"/>
                    <path d="M21 3h-6v18h6V3z"/>
                    <path d="M15 7h-6v14h6V7z"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Proven Track Record</h3>
                <p>I've migrated systems with millions of records. Your project is in safe hands.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="content-block animate-slide-up">
            <h2>My Process</h2>
            <p>
              No 200-page requirements documents. No six-month discovery phases. Here's how I actually work:
            </p>
            <div class="approach-steps">
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Quick Call</h4>
                  <p>15 minutes to understand if I can actually help you</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Real Estimate</h4>
                  <p>You get a price and timeline within 24 hours</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Get It Done</h4>
                  <p>I build it, test it, deploy it. You see progress weekly</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="step">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h4>Actual Support</h4>
                  <p>When something breaks, I fix it. Simple as that</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card glass-card animate-slide-in">
            <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
            <ul class="facts-list">
              <li><strong>Started:</strong> 2024</li>
              <li><strong>Focus:</strong> SAP & BTP only</li>
              <li><strong>Team Size:</strong> Just me</li>
              <li><strong>Response Time:</strong> Same day</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card glass-card animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
            <h3>What I Don't Do</h3>
            <ul class="values-list">
              <li>Salesforce (wrong cloud)</li>
              <li>Oracle (different beast)</li>
              <li>Staff augmentation</li>
              <li>200-person projects</li>
              <li>Meetings about meetings</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card glass-card animate-slide-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <h3>Let's Connect</h3>
            <p>Ready to transform your SAP landscape?</p>
            <a href="mailto:daniel@kinevra.com" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content glass-card">
        <h2 class="gradient-text">Start Your Transformation Journey</h2>
        <p>Partner with Kinevra to unlock the full potential of your SAP investments</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .about-hero {
    padding: 160px 0 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero-content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 80px 0;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .feature-item {
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .feature-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .feature-item p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .approach-steps {
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: white;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .step-content p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .sidebar-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .sidebar-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .facts-list,
  .values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .facts-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .facts-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .values-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .values-list li::before {
    content: 'â†’';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .cta-section {
    padding: 60px 0 100px;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px;
    background: var(--gradient-main);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-content > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .content-sidebar {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-content {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
